name: Goddess Themis by Mael Barbosa
description:
"This art represented by the Goddess Themis, is the oracular Goddess of the Earth, she defends and speaks on behalf of the earth, of the rooting of humanity in an unwavering natural order of connection with the earth and its elements. Themis is at the service of justice in defense of nature against his aggressors who, blinded by power, are destroying our greater good: Our planet!!"
